    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6770454/" class="title-link">后汉书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6770454"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/65285015/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/65285015/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">我是谁</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-07-29"
      class="main-meta">2014-07-29 15:36:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6770454_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  《后汉书》是一部记载东汉历史的纪传体史书，与《史记》、《汉书》、《三国志》合称“四史”。书中分十纪、八十列传和八志(司马彪续作)，记载了从王莽起至汉献帝的195年历史。卷一 光武帝纪第一  卷二 显宗孝明帝纪第二  卷三 肃宗孝章帝纪第三，更多请访问：www.mzyuedu.com

