      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="35432386">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/adultlod/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2539825-18.jpg" alt="長風寓公" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35432386/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35432386/" class="">第999页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/adultlod/" class=" " title="長風寓公">長風寓公</a>
                (資深西吹)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35432386">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">永寿三年十一月，长沙蛮反叛，屯益阳。至延熹三年秋，遂抄掠郡界，众至万余人，杀伤长吏。又零陵蛮入长沙。冬，武陵蛮六千余人寇江陵，荆州刺史刘度、谒者马睦、南郡太守李肃皆奔走。

由此可见楚人苗裔在后汉时，势力依然极大</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-06-22 20:01</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                永寿三年十一月，长沙蛮反叛，屯益阳。至延熹三年秋，遂抄掠郡界，众至万余人，杀伤长吏。又零陵蛮入长沙。冬，武陵蛮六千余人寇江陵，荆州刺史刘度、谒者马睦、南郡太守李肃皆奔走。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>由此可见楚人苗裔在后汉时，势力依然极大
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

